item.title: LIFE DOESN'T SUCK!!! ...I do
item.description:
LIFE DOESN'T SUCK!!! ...I do
This morning I made a list of things that would make life suck less. Every week I upload a 5-minute monologue. Sometimes it's serious. Sometimes it's tongue-in-cheek. I throw everything out there that I wrote during the week. The 'keepers' the crappy jokes & even a few things that I plan on re-writing later into a skit. I think of these videos the way a painter thinks of a sketch book. It's just a bunch of ideas tossed int a vid. Thanks so much to those to take the time to watch & comment! I read all of them! Right now I have no internet. So It's a little tough to write back to everyone. But as soon as my landlord gets it up & running again, I'll try to respond to everyone! Have a fun week! Don't take life too seriously! I hope you like the vids. If not, I hope they inspire you to create your own vids that are better! :) Cheers! - Andrew Hunt
